{
  "stem": "10829.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were very good leaders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we'd seen so much fighting for all this that we know that we didn't want to through that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we wanted to be in Palestine on the land of what we wanted to be.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because anywhere else, we knew we're going to be in programs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We're going to be persecuted again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was our mission at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always felt that you got survived for what?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was our purpose is to go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we finally gave up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we just-- too much of the patriotism, and it was just too much for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So yeah, we could have come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot of families did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we wanted to get there faster.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- but that's enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We want to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother always felt that together we're going to get killed, separated we'd be alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even to this day, when we good to-- when I go to shows or wherever, I try to sit in ends.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Too many Jews, I'm scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother don't like to go to the theaters or other places where there's a lot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, since and she's older, I don't think she thinks of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we never went where there's big Jewish crowds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I used to be active in, which I am in the Yom Ashura and others, one of the first thing, or Yom Kippur or Rosh Hashana, one of the first things when I was in the boards was to make sure we have security police always, no matter what I was active in because of that fear.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Although, I'm not such a Zionist, I don't think I am a Zionist anymore as I used to be.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I still feel I'm [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
